    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six engine. This high-revving power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system for a linear, aggressive power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, ensuring tactile engagement and rear-axle traction. The chassis has been maintained with an eye toward longevity, including a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate floor pan fatigue and refreshed suspension bushings. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul. While displaying minor aesthetic patina consistent with a driven example, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain sharp, offering a pure analog performance experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
