      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior paint retains a beautiful luster, showing only the minor, superficial nicks one would expect from careful road use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the upholstery is free of tears or significant wear, and the dashboard remains crack-free. All electronic components, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has benefited from regular synthetic oil changes and recent brake service. The engine idles quietly and pulls strongly through all gears, while the suspension provides a smooth, rattle-free ride. With a set of high-tread tires and a complete service history included, this car represents a dependable and stylish choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
